caption.body: Creativity Explored @creativityexplored of San Francisco is one of the three pioneering art centers featured in our exhibition "Celebrating a Vision: #ArtAndDisability”. Yesterday, a few artists from the organization made the trip down to the Airport to see their artwork on display in our exhibition. The artists were really excited to see their artwork on display for the enjoyment of so many people at SFO. For more insight on this organization and its extraordinary work, check out this video featuring artist Christina Marie Fong: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Uv1_JUm0sXI
